data.description: Fantastic Loft Condo in the best location of the Perimeter! Top Floor home with open loft floor plan, soaring ceilings, wide plank wood floors, stainless and granite gorgeous kitchen. First class amenities- 24 hour front desk attendants, resort style pool, tennis courts, state of the art fitness center, clubroom, and wine cellar. This home has 2 assigned covered parking spaces side by side and big storage space on the same level as the condo
